# Build outputs must never enter history. artifacts/ held a 78MB APK plus a 104MB base64 copy of
# it, and GitHub hard-rejects any single file over 100MB -- staging them made the first commit
# 377MB. They are reproducible from source, so they are outputs, not inputs.
*.apk
*.aab
*.apk.b64
artifacts/

# A second checkout carrying its own .git; nesting it would either be swallowed as a stray gitlink
# or drag an unrelated history along.
ui-teste-apk-repo/

# Real offer screenshots carry a passenger's pickup address, rating and trip count. See the README
# in that folder; the test that uses them skips when they are absent.
app/src/androidTest/assets/offer-fixtures/*
!app/src/androidTest/assets/offer-fixtures/README.md
